{"tid":1933702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財務相麻生太郎稱不相信中國公布的疫情數據 日本打算與美國合作應對疫情","createTime":"2020-03-19T12:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T16:29:56.000Z","uid":21470,"like":133,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c3327ee4c4b95ab0df4ff89473a37a258b594d0e","tid":1933702,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"麻生太郎稱不相信中國公布的疫情數據<br />\n<br />\n日本財務相麻生太郎表示，他不相信中國公布的新型冠狀病毒疫情數據，但認為病毒是源於中國。麻生在參議院回答議員質詢時指，與2008年的雷曼次按危機不同，看不清今次疫情對實體經濟造成的影響，為應對疫情，日本打算與美國合作，包括交換疫情信息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275055&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1275055%26csid%3D261_367&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFVm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=b523d2fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1275055&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"5f23d63493f9bd3593a28597726315a3515a7c6e","tid":1933702,"uid":41308,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"終於知道支那唔靠得住"},{"pid":"70eb5fa42d4d51168c2a2a0517affd1032b0598a","tid":1933702,"uid":10503,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"美日台 聯盟<br />\n你叫小粉紅情何以堪"},{"pid":"927511046c465b16cdb1858a96dd02bfea3da4e8","tid":1933702,"uid":14494,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:37:37.000Z","msg":"藉機飛起who啦<br />\n侵侵都夠膽鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e77dcd401866ae7f54415058b84560a7b0721a","tid":1933702,"uid":12628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"信果個都岸鳩"},{"pid":"fbc2736ecd7515fbbbe442b7b0c13b4a16cb9d9e","tid":1933702,"uid":237517,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"麻生還麻生<br />\n<br />\n安倍還安倍？"},{"pid":"79e222588f4dda0496878aa5d